snippet.title: Fallen on Steam - Horror Supernatural Action Game
snippet.description:
Get ready for an electrifying experience! "Fallen," the supernatural action horror game, is set to hit #steam in August 2024. 
Unleash your supernatural abilities, battle fierce enemies, and level up to become unstoppable. 

Add it to your wishlist on Steam now!
